  "LINKA_BALLS_BINGO_FEATURE_DESCRIPTION": "Linka-balls is an in-game feature that plays out at the same time as the Bingo Game.   "NO_WIN_FREE_TICKETS_FEATURE_DESCRIPTION": "Don’t worry if you don’t win in the main Bingo game, this room has the No Win Game Entry Tickets feature applied. If you don't win any prizes including features, you will be awarded with Game Entry Tickets for the next game.",

  "PLATINUM_BALL_FEATURE_DESCRIPTION": "This game includes our Platinum Ball feature.   "PRIZE_BINGO_FEATURE_DESCRIPTION": "Prize Bingo awards Full House winner/s a special feature game at the end of the bingo game. Players will randomly select three out of nine prizes which are then revealed. The prize descriptions are detailed on the promotions page of the Gala Bingo website.",
